    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>改写过去，拯救未来。踏入这款刺激的VR射击游戏，生存意味着永生。</strong>操控手中的烈焰凤凰，与命运注定与烈焰风暴绑定的基因强化清洁工杰基并肩作战。你们将携手在崩塌的Slipstream多元宇宙中奋战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>跨越时空的科幻传奇：</strong>从焦土荒原飞向璀璨的未来城市，与灭绝赛跑。每个地点都是战场，也是叙事谜题的一部分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/a48cf42dfcd6b95c9dd0e4b5f0fabf16.poster.avif?t=1771125883\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/a48cf42dfcd6b95c9dd0e4b5f0fabf16.webm?t=1771125883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/a48cf42dfcd6b95c9dd0e4b5f0fabf16.mp4?t=1771125883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>敌人无处不在：</strong>变种人、拾荒者、无人机——无情的敌人潜伏在每个角落。在惊心动魄的VR战斗中杀出一条血路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/f09e69242fd0a941056a3a8eabd59303.poster.avif?t=1771125883\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/f09e69242fd0a941056a3a8eabd59303.webm?t=1771125883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/f09e69242fd0a941056a3a8eabd59303.mp4?t=1771125883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>保护无辜者：</strong>在……以及我们现实之外保护、抓捕、交付并拯救无辜者免受危险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/b64ff6bed7b6ecd4c56d7cab49af3cea.poster.avif?t=1771125883\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/b64ff6bed7b6ecd4c56d7cab49af3cea.webm?t=1771125883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/b64ff6bed7b6ecd4c56d7cab49af3cea.mp4?t=1771125883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>完全沉浸，全情投入：</strong>在这款充满动感的VR射击游戏中，飞行、躲避和射击，体验令人欲罢不能的刺激快感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/a86c06429dfc87fb3cac3af4b2052656.poster.avif?t=1771125883\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/a86c06429dfc87fb3cac3af4b2052656.webm?t=1771125883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/a86c06429dfc87fb3cac3af4b2052656.mp4?t=1771125883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战略射击：</strong>在不同领域之间切换，吸收敌人的子弹，并根据你的意愿扭曲现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/668b2d3c8e9580d07aa57d3abccb3407.poster.avif?t=1771125883\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/668b2d3c8e9580d07aa57d3abccb3407.webm?t=1771125883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/668b2d3c8e9580d07aa57d3abccb3407.mp4?t=1771125883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>增强或毁灭：</strong>收集金色火焰，解锁改变游戏规则的升级：智能炸弹、四联火球、护盾、扩展攻击范围、更快的回复速度和火焰喷射器增强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/77dd2451f0fbd7064dd5b54491ff5bd5.poster.avif?t=1771125883\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/77dd2451f0fbd7064dd5b54491ff5bd5.webm?t=1771125883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246040/extras/77dd2451f0fbd7064dd5b54491ff5bd5.mp4?t=1771125883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超越游戏：</strong>沉浸在VR图书体验中。通过头戴式耳机，阅读和聆听史诗般的反乌托邦科幻小说的第一部。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>感受战斗：</strong>随着传奇作曲家格兰特·柯克霍普创作的欢快配乐移动。使用触觉Tactsuit、TactSleeve和TactVisor增强沉浸感，感受每一次爆炸和打击的震撼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为滑流大师：</strong>立即购买凤凰基因，系好安全带，起飞。非常适合《手枪鞭》、《星际火狐》、《装甲龙骑兵》和《R型》的粉丝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>支持Meta Air/Link和虚拟桌面。对于虚拟桌面，在舒适设置中将水平瞄准角度设置为 +15，以实现最自然的瞄准。</i></p>",
